description:
&lt;p&gt;The Bereavement Support Service is looking for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to join their counselling team. The individual must be able to work flexibly across Carmarthenshire. They must possess a Diploma in Counselling and have extensive experience in grief/end of life work with both adults and children and must be a member of the BACP and have/working towards Accreditation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post. English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 19th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
